image_analysis.description: A photograph of a storage area or office corner. A tall cabinet with wood-grain sides and white doors stands against a wall. On top of the cabinet are two model airplanes. To the right of the cabinet is a stack of white storage boxes, and in the foreground, another stack of white boxes sits on top of a clear plastic bin. A small red rectangular object is mounted high on the wall.
